meanings: (사람·물건 등을) send, (편지 등을) mail[post] (sth to sb), (송금하다) (formal) remit, transfer
send out scouts to see what the enemy is up to
자동차 점검 Could you send an estimate?
자동차 점검 I'd like to see an estimate, please.
